{"title":"狂草","authors":["李发模"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李发模"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽袖，挽起白发苍苍的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"退居家中的闲适"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从历史的砚池中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蘸血、蘸泪、蘸情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还把雄心铺成一张宣纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干戈碰得铿锵的凯旋曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾藏的狼烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊杀的壮志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又棱角方正地，不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而是以血以心泼成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“和平”二字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"末了，掷笔、推砚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那劲头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如当年身为将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把战争逐出人类"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}